Sometimes one just needs to take a moment out of this
crazy, busy world and watch a dachshund channelling his inner drummer while his
owner sings. In the video posted on Facebook,
the four legged pooch can be seen tapping his tail on a rubbish bin while his
owner sings. The video has since garnered more than 46 000 reactions
and was shared over 128 000 times on social media. Watch
the video here: 